The Royal Family marks St Patrick's Day every year, and royal watchers look forward to Kate Middleton and Prince William's traditional visit to Aldershot to watch the 1st Batallion Irish Guards at the St Patrick's Day Parade. Kate often rocks a green outfit for the event, but she is known to love green when out and about on other engagements too. Which is your favourite? Have your say about which outfit Kate looks best in by commenting below.